title: Did CNN issue a correction that Ted's "Kinnon pin " was actually a Doritos chip?
subtitle: Be careful with the footage of the screens on Twitter while travelling without links.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: CNN issued a correction that read: "Ted Cruz was seen wearing a pin with a QANON symbol. He later discovered that this wasn't a QANON pin, but a Doritos snack chip stuck to his suit."
